title: Sort Array By Parity
description: Rearrange the array so that all even integers come before odd integers.

title: Sort Array By Parity II
description: Rearrange the array so that even indices have even numbers and odd indices have odd numbers.

title: Height Checker
description: Count how many indices would change if the array was sorted.

title: Rank Transform of an Array
description: Assign ranks to elements based on their value.

title: Widest Vertical Area Between Two Points Containing No Points
description: Find the maximum width between vertical lines that doesn't contain any points.

title: Sort Array by Increasing Frequency
description: Sort elements by increasing frequency and decreasing value.

title: Number of Equivalent Domino Pairs
description: Count pairs of dominoes that are equivalent.

title: Relative Sort Array
description: Sort an array relative to the order defined by another array.

title: Defanging an IP Address
description: Replace every period '.' in an IP address with '[.]'.

title: Reverse String
description: Reverse the characters of the string in-place.

title: Reverse Vowels of a String
description: Reverse only the vowels in the input string.

title: Contains Duplicate
description: Check if any value appears at least twice in the array.

title: Contains Duplicate II
description: Check for duplicate elements within k distance.

title: Intersection of Two Arrays
description: Return the intersection of two arrays as a set.

title: Intersection of Two Arrays II
description: Return the intersection of two arrays including duplicates.

title: Arithmetic Subarrays
description: Check if each query subarray can form an arithmetic sequence after sorting.

title: Moving Stones Until Consecutive
description: Determine the minimum and maximum number of moves needed to make stones consecutive.
